Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.42,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,This guy's the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:05.00,Chiha-overlap,B,0,0,0,,I've never seen the Queen lose before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:06.61,Chiha-main,C,0,0,0,,He's 4-0 lifetime against the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:09.36,Chiha-main,Ero,0,0,0,,He's no dark horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:12.13,Chiha-main,Ero,0,0,0,,He's a true thoroughbred.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:15.84,Chiha-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Wh-What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:19.06,Chiha-main,Dad,0,0,0,,How are we going to get \Nout of that promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:20.45,Chiha-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:25.08,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0,0,0,,I want you to let me attend \Na university in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.46,Chiha-main,Dad,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:31.21,Chiha-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Let's tell him that he has \Nto win two years in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:33.77,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,There's something I haven't told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:39.97,black1,Caption,0,0,0,,Arata knows about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:38.15,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Grandpa took out an education \Nlife insurance policy for Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.97,black1,Dad,0,0,0,,{\an9}I was left \Nout again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:39.97,Chiha-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Huh?  What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:43.15,Chiha-main,Dad,0,0,0,,B-But aren't you going to \Nmiss having him around?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:46.23,Chiha-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Plus, housing in Tokyo can be \Nridiculously expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:49.29,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,I don't look forward to being \Nalone in the house with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:50.36,Chiha-main,Dad,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:51.83,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:55.00,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Who's going to stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:57.49,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,He's doing what he loves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:00.90,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,and shining at it, all on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.39,0:01:04.70,Chiha-internal,Tai,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:07.75,Chiha-internal,Tai,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:10.84,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0,0,0,,I'll win the individual \Ntournament tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:12.55,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0,0,0,,and go to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:15.21,Chiha-internal,Tai,0,0,0,,He even beat the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:16.80,Chiha-internal,Tai,0,0,0,,He's really going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.98,0:01:23.69,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.27,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Aren't you supposed to \Nhigh-five when you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:26.98,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.67,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,You also won your match, right, Taichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:32.44,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:40.60,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:45.08,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:48.66,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,O-Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:50.71,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:54.34,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,How are you always smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:58.66,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,How are you so calm \Nwhen you play karuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:02.42,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,even when you're up against someone \Nas strong as Shinobu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:04.73,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,How do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.70,0:02:11.86,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,I'm always so intense when I play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:13.75,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:16.83,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,Impassionate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:23.26,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,How does he play karuta that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:28.49,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:29.79,Chiha-overlap,Mura,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:34.04,Chiha-main,Mura,0,0,0,,We need all the champions to \Nassemble on the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.31,Chiha-main,Mura,0,0,0,,Please start moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.31,0:02:38.60,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:47.47,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,I'm working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.37,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,I've worked very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:52.76,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.07,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,Something isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:58.01,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.21,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.28,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,I don't know what the problem is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:05.23,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,but something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:07.66,Chiha-main,Desk,0,0,0,,Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:23.06,Chiha-title2,A,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1800)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:25.82,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,800)}Verse 25
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:25.82,Chiha-ep-title-poem-wide,EpTitle,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,800)}I can\N look up \Nand see \Nthe snowy \Ncap of \NMt. Fuji
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.95,Boxed,Chi,0,0,0,,Class A Champion \N Wataya Arata (2nd Year)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.16,BoxedB,Chi,0,0,0,,Class B Champion \N Mashima Taichi (2nd Year)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:36.88,BoxedC,Chi,0,0,0,,Class C Champion\N Komano Tsutomu (2nd Year)\Nplus 1 other
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.63,BoxedD,Chi,0,0,0,,Class D Champion\N Tsukuba Akihiro (1st Year)\Nplus 3 others
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:41.63,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.54,Chiha-main,Miya,0,0,0,,Everyone did a wonderful job!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:48.89,Chiha-main,Pork,0,0,0,,I figured Ayase's goal of winning \Nevery class was crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.83,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Mizusawa's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:52.51,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,They won Classes B, C, and D.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:54.73,Chiha-main,B,0,0,0,,Should've expected it after they \Nwon the team tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:58.61,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:01.90,this,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,1)}Win every class
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.90,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,It was supposed to go like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.16,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:10.45,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,Everyone else did their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.40,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:17.42,Chiha-main,Sis,0,0,0,,I'll carry your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.09,Chiha-main,Miya,0,0,0,,Everyone have everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.17,Chiha-main,Miya,0,0,0,,Let's get going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.52,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:25.39,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Coach Sakurazawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:30.18,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Would you like video of the Class A final?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.47,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,You have video?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.31,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.25,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:36.06,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,This is my e-mail address.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.84,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.19,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Give me your contact information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.12,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,Chihaya!  We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.11,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:46.11,Chiha-main-top,Ero,0,0,0,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.70,Chiha-main-top,Ero,0,0,0,,Even I don't have her e-mail address!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:47.78,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.70,Ero,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1)}It's dangerous to give Eromu\N that kind of information
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:56.54,Chiha-internal,Saku,0,0,0,,Has anyone else noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.51,Chiha-internal,Saku,0,0,0,,Only two players went through the entire
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:02.67,Chiha-internal,,0,0,0,,high school tournament without a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:05.67,Chiha-internal,Saku,0,0,0,,Wataya Arata from Fukui
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.68,Chiha-internal,Saku,0,0,0,,and Mashima Taichi from Mizusawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:16.06,hospital1,,0,0,0,,Surgical Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.63,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:20.00,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,The same reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.79,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,I can't tell what's wrong, so you'll \Nneed to visit a bigger hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:23.94,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.69,hospital2,,0,0,0,,First General Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:27.79,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.23,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Not again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:32.13,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,I think we need an MRI.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:32.95,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.74,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:41.00,Chiha-main,All,0,0,0,,E-Enchondromatosis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.64,Chiha-main,Desk,0,0,0,,Wh-What does that scary name mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.88,Chiha-main,Pork,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay, Ayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:49.01,Chiha-main,Sumi,0,0,0,,Are your bones going to \Nturn to mush or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.50,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,They ran some tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:56.65,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,and luckily it's only the third \Nbone in my right index finger
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:58.56,Chiha-main,,0,0,0,,where the bone is softening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:04.82,finger,Chi,0,0,0,,{\fad(3000,1)}Only here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:01.63,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,This is a really rare disorder,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:04.82,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,and most people go through their entire \Nlives without knowing they have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.16,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.31,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:12.46,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,I-I'm thinking about having an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:13.62,Chiha-main,All,0,0,0,,An operation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:17.54,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Most people can just ignore it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:21.47,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,but it's recommended that athletes \Nand people who use their hands a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:24.51,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,have an operation to put some \Nfirm material inside the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.63,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,It calls for full anesthesia and \NI'll be hospitalized for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.28,Chiha-main,Pork,0,0,0,,Full anesthesia and hospital time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:31.41,Chiha-main,Tsu,0,0,0,,Isn't it just your finger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:32.82,Chiha-main,Desk,0,0,0,,You can't leave the same day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:40.28,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,B-But I want to be able to play \Nkaruta without having to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.50,Chiha-internal,Tai,0,0,0,,Even injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.69,Chiha-internal,Kana,0,0,0,,...she only cares about karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.40,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Well, at least it's summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.68,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,I need to get going.  You'll be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:55.62,Chiha-main,Chitose,0,0,0,,Take good care of my laptop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.58,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.41,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,We'll come back tomorrow \Nbefore your operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:05.86,dvd,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,375)}Final Match \NWataya vs. Wakamiya
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:12.04,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Young folks have high tech \Nways to kill time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.55,Chiha-main,B,0,0,0,,Isn't that Hundred Poets \Nkaruta, Toko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:22.12,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Why does she look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:24.19,Chiha-main,B,0,0,0,,It's just karuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:32.93,chitosemag,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2350,0)}Ayase Chitose\N{\fs18\c&HEDA8AF&}Second Photo Collection
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:35.96,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Oh, the Millennium is \Ntaken from Chitose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:38.28,chitose,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Chitose --> 1000 Years --> Millennium
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:38.21,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Arata-kun, are you a fan of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:41.17,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,I prefer girls with bigger boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:44.54,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Like, big enough to close you in between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:43.49,phone,A,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,1)}Ayase Chihaya
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.13,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.68,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Oh, you answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:49.46,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.92,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,You actually answer your phone, Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:56.05,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,My sister always ignores me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.43,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.18,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:10.57,Chiha-main,Pork,0,0,0,,She's not really a flower kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:13.00,Chiha-main,Sumi,0,0,0,,Flowers are a must when \Nvisiting someone in the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:15.76,Chiha-main,Sumi,0,0,0,,If I were in her shoes, I would \Nwant flowers as a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.38,Chiha-main,Pork,0,0,0,,Wouldn't food also work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:21.90,Chiha-main,Pork,0,0,0,,She'd probably like chocolate more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:22.75,Chiha-main,Pork,0,0,0,,Or ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.96,Chiha-main,Desk,0,0,0,,I say we go with a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:26.73,Chiha-main,Desk,0,0,0,,This is the perfect opportunity \Nfor her to do some reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:29.27,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,Honestly, just buy whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:31.43,Chiha-main,Pork,0,0,0,,Yes!  Ice cream time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.47,Chiha-main,Sumi,0,0,0,,Wait!  Ice cream is a bad idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:34.32,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.05,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.27,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Do you want any flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:42.18,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,Can I get some flowers that \Nare a cheerful color?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.40,Chiha-internal,Tai,0,0,0,,She's probably feeling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:51.07,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Simply put, I want to \Nget better at karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.44,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,That's simple, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.65,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,That's all I can think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:59.91,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,I've been working really \Nhard for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:06.32,Chiha-internal,Ara,0,0,0,,We aren't even playing, \Nand you're already fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:15.88,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:22.15,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.93,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,The cicadas are loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:28.20,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,I feel like we're in different countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.84,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,Even though we can talk over the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:34.18,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,he's so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:49.82,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,You know, whether it's an official \Nmatch or a practice match,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.63,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,I always go back to that \Nroom when I'm playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:58.07,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,That room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:06.14,Chiha-flashback,Gran,0,0,0,,When did you have the \Nmost fun playing karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:10.10,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Where I was never scared, \Nno matter who came in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:13.90,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Where I was always happy, having fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:16.53,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,and wishing it'd never end...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:21.61,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Back when you and I played karuta \Nin that old apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.80,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,Back in that old
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.80,Chiha-internal,,0,0,0,,apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.50,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0,0,0,,Wow, this place is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:44.55,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0,0,0,,L-Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:47.09,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0,0,0,,If you become the best player in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:49.24,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0,0,0,,you'll be the best in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:53.85,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,The time we spent playing there \Nis making Arata stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.80,Chiha-main,Pork,0,0,0,,This hospital is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:58.70,Chiha-overlap,Tsu,0,0,0,,Whew, it's so cool inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.70,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,Sorry, Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.86,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,We ran late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.74,Chiha-main,Desk,0,0,0,,It's too hot outside today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.47,Chiha-main,Pork,0,0,0,,The chocolate's melting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.82,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:12.78,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,I don't understand these feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:15.70,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:18.13,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,For the rest of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:20.77,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,I'll always love karuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:26.00,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1)}the red that is the Tatsuta River
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:24.42,Chiha-internal,chi,0,0,0,,and I'll always love Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.15,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,The operation was a success,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:32.06,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,so you just have the \Npain to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:34.47,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,We'll keep an eye on it and, \Nif everything looks okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:36.41,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,you'll be discharged \Nin a week as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:38.22,Chiha-main,B,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:42.90,nervous,Caption,0,0,0,,Nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.90,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,No practice swings until the cast is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.81,Chiha-main,Chitose,0,0,0,,Is this going to leave a scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:47.68,Chiha-main,Chitose,0,0,0,,Yikes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.63,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Stop that, Chitose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.66,Chiha-main-top,Chitose,0,0,0,,And your summer vacation is ruined...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:50.66,Chiha-main,Mom,0,0,0,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.96,Chiha-main,Chitose,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.91,Chiha-main,Chitose,0,0,0,,Try to finish your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:00.17,Chiha-main,Chitose,0,0,0,,Oh, this is a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.03,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Doing homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.13,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.89,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,That's very responsible of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.43,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.16,writing2,Kana,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,267)\an7\fs22}Year 2 Classical Literature\NSpecial Assignment\NCompose 20 poems
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.84,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0,0,0,,Chihaya-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:17.69,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0,0,0,,It's not difficult to compose poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:23.52,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0,0,0,,You just have to translate \Nyour feelings into meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:26.16,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.79,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0,0,0,,You must be able to read poetry \Nbefore you can compose poetry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.03,Chiha-card-TS,Kana,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1)}Compose
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:37.96,Chiha-card-TS,Kana,0,0,0,,Compose \NRead
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:37.96,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0,0,0,,I believe that amateurs can only \Nunderstand 50% of verbal poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:41.29,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0,0,0,,When written out in modern \Nlanguage, it goes down to 30%.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.42,Chiha-flashback,,0,0,0,,If the poem is written in classical language,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:45.97,Chiha-flashback,,0,0,0,,only 10% of the meaning is understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.33,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0,0,0,,You must accept that \Nyou don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:49.78,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0,0,0,,{\a6}V-Verbal?  Cl-Classical?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.78,Chiha-flashback,,0,0,0,,what you think you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:52.82,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0,0,0,,I recommend you start \Nby reading these books!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:54.57,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0,0,0,,N-Not happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:59.73,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,I managed to compose five poems \Nin a rush before July ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:13.47,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,I want to play karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:20.51,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0,0,0,,I always go back to that \Nroom when I'm playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.06,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0,0,0,,If you become the best player in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:31.13,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0,0,0,,you'll be the best in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:38.22,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,Ever since meeting Arata,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:43.24,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,my life has been all about karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.42,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,Always striving to become stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.58,Chiha-internal,,0,0,0,,and stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:53.75,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,so I can be able
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:56.98,Chiha-internal,,0,0,0,,to receive his passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:02.75,nurse station,A,0,0,0,,Nurse Station
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:02.75,reception,A,0,0,0,,Reception
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:02.75,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Please return these to the \Nreceptionist when you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.08,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:05.08,badges,Kana,0,0,0,,{\fad(501,1)}Visitor 32 \N\NVisitor 33
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.04,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,Here you are, Prez.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:13.09,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.92,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,You're working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:17.74,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,Is that your summer homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:18.52,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.67,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,Is it okay for you to be moving around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.11,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,You can hold off on the twenty poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:28.44,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,In the sweltering summer sunlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.56,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,I feast upon a whirlwind of ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:35.46,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,Since I could not stop \Nthinking of Shinobu-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:38.25,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,I wonder if she is \Npracticing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.25,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.22,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,Were you actually trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:43.20,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,Your grade will drop for every \None of these you turn in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.36,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,What?  Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.13,black,Chi,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:56.64,Poem,Chi,0,0,0,,6\NInside a room isolated \Nfrom the summer heat,\NI feel bliss \Nupon hearing your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:51.78,Chiha-internal,,0,0,0,,Inside a room isolated \Nfrom the summer heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.94,Chiha-internal,,0,0,0,,I feel bliss upon hearing your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:00.85,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,How's your finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:01.84,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:03.94,Chiha-main,,0,0,0,,I don't remember a thing\Nafter I was knocked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.33,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,but I needed four stitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:16.06,Poem - White,Chi,0,0,0,,7\NWill I ever turn the \Ncorner and find you?\NI can only wait for \Na dream or a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:11.61,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,Will I ever turn the corner and find you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:15.61,Chiha-internal,Chi,0,0,0,,I can only wait for a dream or a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:31.35,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,She's doing better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:34.76,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,It looks like the operation\N was a success, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:38.28,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,She should recover in time \Nfor the fall tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.19,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,What is it, Oe-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.32,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,You have to try harder, Prez!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:02.86,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,You don't have to invite me along \Nwhen you visit her in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.67,Chiha-main,Kana,0,0,0,,You can't expect Chihaya-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.02,Chiha-main,,0,0,0,,to be clueless for the rest of her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:20.83,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:41.22,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Ayase-san!  No practice swings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.34,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:43.67,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:46.83,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:56.21,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:57.84,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Be careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:18:01.22,Chiha-main,Ero,0,0,0,,Coach, it's getting dark, \Nso I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.39,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.89,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,If I'm around you too much, I'm \Nafraid I'll have dreams about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:07.16,Chiha-main,Ero,0,0,0,,I'd want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:09.19,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,And why are you here when \Nyou've already left the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.11,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.65,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Coach Sakurazawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.87,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Oh, Ayase-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:19.30,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for sending \Nthe DVD of the high school final!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.48,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Was it useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:23.39,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Yes, I've been watching it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:25.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I got to see what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:26.54,Chiha-main,,0,0,0,,at the start of the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.69,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Both players were incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:30.54,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,I saw Arata—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:35.30,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,I saw Wataya-kun play for the \Nfirst time, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:36.30,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:41.04,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,What were your thoughts on \Nthat match, Coach Sakurazawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:43.95,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:48.77,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Wataya-kun had a very \Nbalanced play style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.68,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,There's nothing special \Nabout his game sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:54.53,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,but he was consistent and caught \Nevery partial syllable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:56.86,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,I would guess he's a right \Nbrain memorizer,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:01.03,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,but he also uses his left brain, so \Nfatigue isn't as much of a factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:04.03,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,The Queen is also special.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:07.19,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,I'd love to know how she \Nconnects to the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:11.80,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,She appears to be apologizing \Nwhen she moves cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.53,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Her connection to the cards is very deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.84,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Plus, she isn't afraid of committing faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.64,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Her playing style reflects her \Ntrust in her own karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:22.72,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.14,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,I got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:26.00,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,No, that was very educational!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.09,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,It helps a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:28.96,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:35.25,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Ayase-san, would you be interested in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.23,Chiha-main,,0,0,0,,participating in a Fujisaki \Ntwo-day karuta camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:40.86,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Along with the president and \Nother players from Mizusawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:44.78,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,I'll come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.41,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,I just had an operation on my \Nright hand, but I'll come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:49.03,Chiha-main,Saku,0,0,0,,Operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.13,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,H-Here we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:57.88,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:03.55,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,I wish the other players \Ncould have joined us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:07.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped that the Suihoku \Nsociety has its camp at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:11.04,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan and Tsukuba-kun \Nare also busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:17.19,Chiha-internal,Kana,0,0,0,,Prez, I'll deal with the first-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.88,Chiha-internal,Kana,0,0,0,,It has to be the two of you \Ngoing to Shizuoka alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:26.70,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,Anyway, are you sure \Nabout this, Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.89,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,You were told not to do any \Nphysical activity for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.47,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:37.21,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,but I've never gone such a long \Ntime without playing karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:42.08,Chiha-main,Chi,0,0,0,,It's hard when I can't \Nthink of anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:52.90,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,Forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:58.20,Chiha-main,Tai,0,0,0,,We can only move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:01.90,Chiha-main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:31.41,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Huh?  Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:32.62,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:35.95,Chiha-main,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping to get a karuta scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:38.54,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,After winning the high \Nschool championship,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:40.42,Chiha-main,,0,0,0,,I have permission from my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:42.15,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Wait, Arata-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:43.60,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Don't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:46.51,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do without you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:47.83,Chiha-main,Ara,0,0,0,,I'm not quitting right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:49.97,Chiha-main,A,0,0,0,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:51.05,Chiha-overlap,Ara,0,0,0,,I'm not quitting yet!
